Polymorphism:Many ways to perform anything

types of polymorphism:
1)Method Overloading:When two methods having a same name but number of parameters are diffrent


2)Method Overriding:When two methods having a same name and number of parameters are also same


StringBuilder & StringBuffer

StringBuilder -Immutable - can not change the value
StringBuffer - Mutable -can change the value

================================================

How to Declare strings:
1)Literal String
2)New Keyword String
3)Character Array String

